Name: Max
Owner: rye.brows
Summary: Wow what a glorious chonk. Why he looking like a pillow case filled with too much candy on Halloween? THIS MAN BOUT TO BURST. Just kidding, Max is working very hard to lose weight and it is difficult due to a metabolic issue😢 we are all so proud of your journey so far Max!!
•
He’s down about 4 pounds and on a very strict diet!

Name: Kitkat
Owner: @morganbmeyer 
Summary: Kitkat was caught completely zoned out of reality. She will watch tv and believe she is actually there. She will claw, lick, and jump at your tv. She has jumped through 6 tvs putting a perfect circle right in the middle. Kitkat has cost her owners thousands.
•
Kitkat is on a diet and it’s going well!
